eters, it appears unlikely that recurrent novae can provide a significant\nchannel for the production of Type Ia supernovae.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Dec 2014 23:29:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
