low us to derive tight confidence intervals for the Good--Turing estimator of\nthe missing mass.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Dec 2014 15:20:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2015 15:27:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2016 13:49:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-29"}
